c: 60
v: 11
t: "Nihagira umwe mu bagore banyu ubacika akajya mu bahakanyi (ntibabasubize inkwano mwabatanzeho), hanyuma habaho impamvu yo kurwana nabo mukabatsinda (mukagira iminyago mubakuraho), mujye muha abo abagore babo bagiye ibingana n’ibyo babatanzeho (inkwano). Kandi mutinye Allah we mwemera"